R:"\\(A\\) is a \\(3 \\times 1\\) matrix. Its transpose \\(A^t\\) will have order \\(1 \\times 3\\)."
}

q {
Q:"If \\(n\\) is any positive integer then \\(4^n > 3^n + \\dots\\) is true for all:"
A:"c"
O:a) "\\(n \\leq 2\\)", b) "\\(n < 3\\)", c) "\\(n > 2\\)", d) "\\(n \\geq 2\\)"
